    {
      "scene_id": "voice-scene-02",
      "section_id": "voice-section-02",
      "sentence_id": "sentence-03",
      "sentence": "Sample data: Liverpool have started quickly in recent home matches, while Arsenal have sometimes needed longer to settle away.",
      "start": 3.42,
      "end": 10.9,
      "estimated_duration": 7.48
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "voice-scene-03",
      "section_id": "voice-section-03",
      "sentence_id": "sentence-04",
      "sentence": "So the real question is: Can Arsenal survive Liverpool's fast start?",
      "start": 11.54,
      "end": 15.91,
      "estimated_duration": 4.37
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "voice-scene-03",
      "section_id": "voice-section-03",
      "sentence_id": "sentence-05",
      "sentence": "Liverpool usually start aggressively, pressing high and forcing rushed decisions.",
      "start": 15.94,
      "end": 19.88,
      "estimated_duration": 3.94
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "voice-scene-03",
      "section_id": "voice-section-03",
      "sentence_id": "sentence-06",
      "sentence": "Arsenal have enough quality to play through it, but a messy opening can drag them from their plan.",
      "start": 19.91,
      "end": 26.97,
      "estimated_duration": 7.07
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "voice-scene-03",
      "section_id": "voice-section-03",
      "sentence_id": "sentence-07",
      "sentence": "The evidence is simple: Liverpool usually make opponents uncomfortable early at home.",
      "start": 27.0,
      "end": 31.72,
      "estimated_duration": 4.73
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "voice-scene-03",
      "section_id": "voice-section-03",
      "sentence_id": "sentence-08",
      "sentence": "The balance matters too: Arsenal may be better prepared for pressure than older form suggests.",
      "start": 31.75,
      "end": 37.65,
      "estimated_duration": 5.9
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "voice-scene-03",
      "section_id": "voice-section-03",
      "sentence_id": "sentence-09",
      "sentence": "That makes it a slight home edge, not a prediction.",
      "start": 37.68,
      "end": 41.62,
      "estimated_duration": 3.94
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "voice-scene-03",
      "section_id": "voice-section-03",
      "sentence_id": "sentence-10",
      "sentence": "Watch the opening phase closely; it may tell you how the rest of the game will unfold.",
      "start": 41.65,
      "end": 48.33,
      "estimated_duration": 6.68
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "voice-scene-04",
      "section_id": "voice-section-04",
      "sentence_id": "sentence-11",
      "sentence": "The x-factor is arsenal's ability to escape liverpool's first press.",
      "start": 48.83,
      "end": 52.74,
      "estimated_duration": 3.92
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "voice-scene-04",
      "section_id": "voice-section-04",
      "sentence_id": "sentence-12",
      "sentence": "Can Arsenal survive the first 20 minutes, or will Liverpool take control early?",
      "start": 52.77,
      "end": 57.92,
